{"tid":1449134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T18:28:48.000Z","uid":207295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"20c0187b1ce7b9bdf5f5e4e3359c7f3e583813ae","tid":1449134,"uid":207295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:47:53.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=836411fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=585ffcb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"95cc206cf7ab407745688f94dce94d21ba46eb0a","tid":1449134,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4815f95c82d2f93fc523ab8f119ac0a2d0b6210f","tid":1449134,"uid":207295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95cc206cf7ab407745688f94dce94d21ba46eb0a","tid":1449134,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T18:28:48.000Z","msg":"羅sir你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}